author: danielf
msg: * Moved actions, modules, some sources, matchers, selectors and the StatusGenerator to the cocoon-sitemap-components module.
* Moved various abstract and helper classes for the above kind of components and the components.flow package to the cocoon-sitemap-impl module.

* Moved the util.jxpath package to the cocoon-sitemap-impl package which probably isn't the right place for it, but I didn't want to make cocoon-util dependent on jxpath, as that would mean that about everything would depend on jxpath.
* Moved the rest of the util package to cocoon-util.
There are still classes left in cocoon-core, where more thinking is needed about where to put them. Tests and configuration files are not moved yet.
